(1, 'Osprey Daylite Plus 20L Travel Pack Beryl Blue', 'OSPREY-407-BB', '<p>Traveling can be difficult but the Daylite makes it easier. With protected, padded storage for a laptop, and just enough organization to keep you moving through the terminal, it\'s the travel companion you never leave behind.</p>', '<p>The Daylite Series started out with humble beginnings, a simple accessory to attach to our larger packs. However, its lightweight, simplicity, durability, comfortable carry and price has proven to be wildly popular, and today their popularity is undeniable. While the Daylite and Daylite Plus continue to serve well as add-on packs for traveling and more, they shine on their own with incredible versatility and are now available in an even more robust color palette than before.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Main</strong> - 210D Nylon Double Diamond Ripstop</p>\r\n<p><strong>Accent</strong> - 400HD Nylon Packcloth</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bottom</strong> - 400HD Nylon Packcloth</p>\r\n', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong> <ul> <li>Large panel-loading main compartment</span></li> <li>Attaches to a variety of compatible Osprey packs</span></li> <li>Side mesh pockets</span></li> <li>Front pocket with mesh organizer and key clip</span></li> <li>Spacermesh shoulder straps with integrated handle</span></li> <li>Multi-function interior sleeve for hydration or tablet</span></li> <li>Mesh-covered backpanel with slotted foam</span></li> </ul>', '3250.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/Osprey_Daylite_Plus_20L_Travel_Pack_Beryl_Blue_1.jpg\r\n', 'Osprey Daylite Plus 20L Travel Pack Beryl Blue', 'Traveling can be difficult but the Osprey Daylite Plus 20L Travel Pack makes it easier', 'osprey, hiking, manila outdoors, backpack', 2, 3, '2018-01-26 08:24:44'),
(2, 'Ticket to the moon Double Hammock Turquoise / Green', 'TMD1411', '<p>Ticket to the Moon make leight travel hammocks of parachute silk. This breathable nylon dries fast and can be washed. The hammock is packed in a small pouch which is sewed on the hammock and can also be used to put small things in it.</p>', '<p>That is the freedom of today. No luxury, no time planner, only nature, your hammock and you. And if you are on the road \r\nyou appreciate leight luggage. That is why the Ticket to the Moon founder had the idea to create a light weight travel hammock. \r\nThe result are today\'s Ticket to the Moon travel hammocks made of parachute silk. This functional material is not only light but \r\nalso breathable, soft to the skin and washable. You can take this Ticket to the Moon light hammock everywhere, for the holidays, a weekend trip or on a boat for instance. Carrying bag included.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications:</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Load Capacity: </strong>200 kg - 440 lbs<br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong>Turquoise / Green<br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong>600 g/1.3 lbs<br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong>320 x 200 cm/10.5 x 6.5 ft<br></p>\r\n', ' <strong><p class=\"orange\">Features:</p></strong>  <ul> <li>The parachute hammock was made by travellers for travellers. </li> <li>A comfortable sleep and ideal protection from insects and small reptiles. </li> <li>It can replace your tent: lightweight, strong, and foldable.</li> <li>The hammock sets up in less than a minute. </li> <li>Is rot-resistant and quick to dry (machine washable 30&deg;Â°C). </li> <li>Ideal for camping, trekking and any outdoor activities.</li> </ul>', '3200.00', 12, 'assets/img/products/Ticket_to_the_moon_Double_Hammock_Turquoise_Green_1.jpg', 'Ticket to the moon Double Hammock Turquoise / Green', 'Ticket to the Moon make light travel hammocks of parachute silk. This breathable nylon dries fast and can be washed. ', 'hammock, ticket to the moon, manila outdoors, sleeping gear, camping gear', 5, 4, '2018-01-26 08:26:00'),
(3, 'Craghoppers Kimba Lite Men\'s Jacket - Royal Navy', 'CMW694-RN', '<p>The Kimba jacket is constructed from a highly durable yet breathable fabric with Craghoppers innovative AquaDry membrane technology for an optimal performance in all weather conditions. </p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications:</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> Royal Navy<br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight:</strong> 750 g<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"orange\"><strong>Please refer to the images for the sizing guide</strong></p>\r\n<img src=\"assets/img/catalog/craghoppers-sizing-guide.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\">\r\n', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features:</p></strong> <ul> <li>Waterproof, windproof,breathable Aquadry</li> <li>fabric</li> <li>Stylish cut</li> <li>Reflective trim</li> <li>Drawcorded hood</li> <li>Zippered pockets</li> <li>Hem Drawcord</li> <li>Map pocket</li> <li>Hook and Loop adjustable cuffs</li> <li>Packable</li> </ul>', '7300.00', 0, 'assets/img/products/Craghoppers_Kimba_Lite_Mens_Jacket_Royal_Navy_1.jpg', 'Craghoppers Kimba Lite Men\'s Jacket - Royal Navy', 'The Craghoppers Kimba Lite Men\'s Jacket - Royal Navy is constructed from a highly durable yet breathable fabric with CraghoppersÃ¢â¬â¢s innovative AquaDry membrane technology for an optimal performance in all weather conditions. ', 'craghoppers, kimba, kimba jacket, hiking apparel, manila outdoors', 1, 6, '2018-01-26 08:30:00'),
(4, 'Vargo Titanium Spoon / Fork / Knife Set', 'T-216', '<p>Slightly lighter than our standard campware set, the ULV version features a matte finish and narrow design.</p>', '<p>The Vargo Titanium Spoon/Fork/Knife Set - ULV (U.ltra L.ight V.ersion) features a smaller, narrower design to make them lighter than our standard Titanium Spoon/Fork/Knife Set.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications:</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong>38 grams <br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Size: </strong>15.2cm </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features:</p></strong> <ul> <li>Matte finish</li> <li>Made of pure titanium</li> <li>Biocompatible</li> <li>Lighter than Lexan utensils</li> <li>Each piece weighs less than 0.5 ounces (14 grams)</li> <li>Mini carabiner included</li> </ul>', '1600.00', 24, 'assets/img/products/Vargo_Titanium_Spoon_Fork_Knife_Set_1.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Spoon / Fork / Knife Set', 'Slightly lighter than our standard campware set, the Vargo Titanium Spoon / Fork / Knife Set version features a matte finish and narrow design.', 'vargo, hiking, camping cutlery, spoon, fork', 4, 1, '2018-01-26 08:33:41'),
(10, 'Ferrino Backpack Triolet 32+5 Blue', '75581CBB', '<p>4 season mountaineering backpack equipped with all technical details for that activity, front access</p>', '<p>Mountaineering backpack with special technical and ergonomic features which makes it a product of outstanding quality appropriate for every mountaineering activity.</p> \r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong> \r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Blue</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 32+5L</p>\r\n<p><strong>Minimum Weight: </strong> 1000 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Maximum Weight: </strong> 1500 g</p>\r\n', ' <strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p> </strong> <ul>   <li>420D HD invisible ripstop</li>   <li>Reinforcement in Hypalon </li> </ul>  <strong><p class=\"orange\">Carrying System</p></strong> <ul>   <li>ACT back</li>   <li>Removable back panel reinforced by an adjustable duralluminium bar</li>   <li>Upper adjustment for shoulder straps</li>   <li>Padded and ergonomic shoulder straps and waist band in breathable mesh fabric</li>   <li>Waist band with removable wings to be used with climbing harness </li></ul><strong><p class=\"orange\">Pockets</p></strong> <ul>   <li>Pocket onlid</li>   <li>Safety pocket</li>   <li>Small pocket on waist band</li>   <li>Side pockets in mesh fabric</li>   <li>Shovel/probe holder pocket </li> </ul>  <strong><p class=\"orange\">Accessories</p></strong><ul> <li>Front access to the backpack main compartment</li> <li>Extensible body &#40;+5 l&#41;</li> <li>Ski holders on the sides</li> <li>Two ice axe holders</li> <li>Loops to hold gears on the outside, inside and on waist band</li> <li>Side compression straps</li> <li>Strap to hold rope on lid</li> <li>Compatible with H2 bag</li> <li>Removable straps to hold snow shoes/snow board</li> <li>Chest strap with emergency whistle</li> <li>SOS instructions</li></ul>', '6500.00', 5, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-backpack-triolet-32-5-blue.jpg', 'Ferrino Backpack Triolet 32+5 Blue', 'Ferrino Backpack Triolet 32+5 Blue is a 4 season mountaineering backpack equipped with all technical details for that activity, front access', 'ferrino, backpack, hiking, mountaineering, rucksack', 2, 2, '2018-01-26 17:22:42'),
(11, 'Ferrino Sleepingbag Yukon Plus', '86357BBD', '<p>Made with filling in H.T.F. High Thermal Perfomance for its high performance that comes from a blend of two hollow fibers with different characteristics.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p> </strong>\r\n<p><strong>EXT.: </strong> 100% Polyester 210T Ripstop</p>\r\n<p><strong>INNER: </strong> Polyester Pongee 240T</p>\r\n<p><strong>FILLING: </strong> 200 g/m2 HTF Perfomance &#40;2 layers&#41;</p> \r\n\r\n', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong><ul> <li>Cold protection hood </li> <li>Zip baffle and padded heat collar </li> <li>2-way combinable zips </li> <li>Two ice axe holders</li> <li>Storage pocket </li> <li>Offset seams: to prevent heat dispersion,<br>the seams between the inner and outer layers are never communicating</li> <li>Sack with double protection closure/extension. </li></ul>', '3100.00', 4, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-sleepingbag-yukon-plus.jpg', 'Ferrino Sleepingbag Yukon Plus', 'Ferrino Sleepingbag Yukon Plus is made with filling in H.T.F. High Thermal Perfomance for its high performance that comes from a blend of two hollow fibers with different characteristics.', 'ferrino, sleeping bag, camping hiking, manila outdoors', 6, 2, '2018-01-26 17:29:37'),
(12, 'Ferrino Fitzroy Backpack 22L Black', '75580CCC', '<p>4 seasons mountaineering backpack equipped with RECCO reflector</p>', '<p>Multipurpose backpack, equipped with many accessories, appropriate for all mountaineering activities.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 1100 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 22L</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>420D HD invisible ripstop</li>\r\n  <li>SupertexÂ®  </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Carrying System</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>D.E.A. Back panel</li>\r\n  <li>Ultra-breathable back in mesh fabric</li>\r\n  <li>Upper adjustment for shoulder straps</li>\r\n  <li>Ergonomic, padded and quilted shoulder straps and waist belt in breathable mesh fabric</li>\r\n  <li>Load lifter </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Pockets</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Double pocket in top lid</li>\r\n  <li>Security pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Front and side bellows pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Pocket in waist belt</li>\r\n  <li>Inside pocket in back</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accesssories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Front access to main backpack compartment</li>\r\n  <li>Double bellows bottom with front access</li>\r\n  <li>Removable top lid that converts to a small backpack</li>\r\n  <li>Side compression tapes</li>\r\n  <li>Two ice axe/pole holders</li>\r\n  <li>Removable gear straps on bottom</li>\r\n  <li>Loops in top lid</li>\r\n  <li>Backpack cover</li>\r\n  <li>Compatible with H2 bag hydration control system</li>\r\n</ul>', '9800.00', 5, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-fitzroy-22-black.jpg', 'Ferrino Fitzroy Backpack 22L Black', 'Ferrino Fitzroy 22 Black is a 4 seasons mountaineering backpack equipped with RECCO reflector', 'ferrino, fitzroy, backpack, rucksack', 2, 2, '2018-01-26 18:27:53'),
(13, 'Ferrino Backpack Finisterre 48 Black', '75735BRR', '<p>Linear backpack complete with all equipment. The D.N.S back is a guarantee of perfect ventilation.</p>', '<p>Ideal backpack for excursions, it has a slim shape and it is equipped with all accessories. D.N.S. dry net system allows for perfect ventilation of your back.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 1650 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 48 L</p>', '\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabrics</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Diamond HD</li>\r\n  <li>SupertexÂ® </li>\r\n  <li>Dupont HypalonÂ® reinforcements </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Carrying System</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>D.N.S. back</li>\r\n  <li>Load lifter</li>\r\n  <li>Upper adjustment for shoulder straps</li>\r\n  <li>Ergonomic, padded and quilted shoulder straps and waist belt in breathable mesh fabric</li>\r\n  <li>Load lifter </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Pockets</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Pocket in top lid</li>\r\n  <li>Safety pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Bellows front pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Bellows side pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Pocket on waist belt</li>\r\n  <li>Back side inner pocket</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Accesssories</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Folding double bottom with front access</li>\r\n  <li>Compression straps</li>\r\n  <li>Two ice-axe/stick holder</li>\r\n  <li>Compatible with the H2 bag hydration control system</li>\r\n  <li>Loops on top lid</li>\r\n  <li>Removable straps for snowshoes/snowboard</li>\r\n  <li>Loops in top lid</li>\r\n  <li>Backpack cover</li>\r\n  <li>Removable gear straps on the bottom</li>\r\n</ul>', '5200.00', 6, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-backpack-finisterre-48-black.jpg', 'Ferrino Backpack Finisterre 48 Black', 'Ferrino Backpack Finisterre 48 Black is a inear backpack complete with all equipment. The D.N.S back is a guarantee of perfect ventilation.', 'ferrino, fitzroy, rucksack, manila outdoors', 2, 2, '2018-01-26 18:39:18'),
(14, 'Osprey Aether Anti-Gravity 70L Rucksack', '10000688-AD-M', '<p>Winner of Outside Magazine\'s Gear of the Year Award for 2017, the Aether AGâ¢ 70 is the perfect backpacking solution when your primary concerns are carrying heavy loads in ventilated comfort for bigger trips and weeklong-plus excursions. Now featuring our innovative Anti-Gravityâ¢ technology and custom fit along with an incredibly robust feature set and a top lid that converts to a functional daypack or summit pack.</p>', '<p>For backpacking, thru-hikes and alpine expeditions, the Aether AGâ¢ Series has a pedigree like no other pack. We set the bar for technical backpacking packs by combining Anti-Gravityâ¢ technology with customizable fit and innovative features to create a more capable and comfortable pack for long-haul load carrying on any multi-day excursion.When you need a pack that can carry heavy loads for up to a week or more, there is no better option than the Aether AGâ¢ 70. Size XL comes with a Large hipbelt and harness.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Adirondack Green</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 2365 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 70 L</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 85 x  40 x 34 cm</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Built in Raincover</li>\r\n  <li>Dual upper side compression straps</li>\r\n  <li>Dual access side stretch mesh pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Lower Inside-Outâ¢ compression straps</li>\r\n  <li>Zippered hipbelt pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Stow-on-the-Goâ¢ trekking pole attachment</li>\r\n  <li>Additional main compartment access</li>\r\n  <li>Large stretch mesh front panel pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Dual front compression straps with StraightJacketâ¢ compression</li>\r\n  <li>Dual ice tool loops with bungee tie-offs</li>\r\n  <li>Zippered sleeping bag compartment with removable divider</li>\r\n  <li>Removable sleeping pad straps</li>\r\n  <li>Integrated FlapJacketâ¢ cover for lidless use</li>\r\n  <li>Internal hydration reservoir sleeve</li>\r\n  <li>Large front J-zip access to main compartment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabric</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>210D Nylon Dobby</li>\r\n  <li>210D High Tenacity Nylon Shadow Box</li>\r\n  <li>500D Nylon Packcloth</li>\r\n</ul>', '17300.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/osprey-aether-anti-gravity-70l-rucksack.jpg', 'Osprey Aether Anti-Gravity 70L Rucksack', 'Osprey Aether Anti-Gravity 70L Rucksack is the perfect backpacking solution when your primary concerns are carrying heavy loads for weeklong-plus excursions.', 'osprey, aether, anti-gravity, rucksack, backpack', 2, 3, '2018-01-26 19:18:10'),
(15, 'Osprey Stratos 24L Hiking Backpack Black', '10000812-BK', '<p>Like carrying a breeze on your back, this incredibly ventilated pack features panel-loading convenience and organization for demanding day hikes and features adjustable torso lengths to dial in the perfect fit for everyone.</p>', '<p>The supremely ventilated, featured and durable Stratos Series receives a makeover that is more than skin deep for Spring 2017. Now featuring adjustable torso lengths for improved fit and comfort with updated aesthetics, the Stratos 24 is the go-to choice for those who prefer panel-loading organization on day hikes in wet or hot environments where staying dry and keeping your cool matter most. When the weather turns, fear not - Stratos keeps your gear and pack protected with an integrated raincover. Smartly organized pocketing keeps all your equipment where you need it, when you need.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Black</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 1250 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 24 L</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 59 x 30 x 30 cm</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Front panel storage pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Front panel vertical center zippered pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Large top panel zippered slash pocket</li>\r\n  <li>Dual side compression straps</li>\r\n  <li>Stow-on-the-Go&trade; trekking pole attachment</li>\r\n  <li>Dual side stretch mesh pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Ice tool loop with bungee tie-off</li>\r\n  <li>Integrated raincover</li>\r\n  <li>Zippered hipbelt pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Internal hydration reservoir sleeve</li>\r\n  <li>Dual-zippered panel access to main compartment</li>\r\n  <li>Large top panel zippered slash pocket</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabric</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Main: 210D Nylon Crosshatch</li>\r\n  <li>Accent: 420HD Nylon Packcloth</li>\r\n  <li>Bottom: 420HD Nylon Packcloth</li>\r\n</ul>', '8