(16, 'Osprey Daylite Plus 20L Travel Pack Real Red', '10000407-RR', '<p>Traveling can be difficult but the Daylite makes it easier. With protected, padded storage for a laptop, and just enough organization to keep you moving through the terminal, it\'s the travel companion you never leave behind.</p>', '<p>The Daylite Series started out with humble beginnings, a simple accessory to attach to our larger packs. However, its lightweight, simplicity, durability, comfortable carry and price has proven to be wildly popular, and today their popularity is undeniable. While the Daylite and Daylite Plus continue to serve well as add-on packs for traveling and more, they shine on their own with incredible versatility and are now available in an even more robust color palette than before.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Real Red</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 453 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 20 L</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 45.7 x  25.4 x 22.9 cm</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Large panel-loading main compartment</li>\r\n  <li>Attaches to a variety of compatible Osprey packs</li>\r\n  <li>Side mesh pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Front pocket with mesh organizer and key clip</li>\r\n  <li>Spacermesh shoulder straps with integrated handle</li>\r\n  <li>Multi-function interior sleeve for hydration or tablet</li>\r\n  <li>Mesh-covered backpanel with slotted foam</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabric</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Main: 210D Nylon Double Diamond Ripstop</li>\r\n  <li>Accent: 400HD Nylon Packcloth</li>\r\n  <li>Bottom: 400HD Nylon Packcloth</li>\r\n</ul>', '3300.00', 5, 'assets/img/products/osprey-daylite-plus-20l-travel-pack-real-red.jpg', 'Osprey Daylite Plus 20L Travel Pack Real Red', 'Traveling can be difficult but the Osprey Daylite Plus 20L Travel Pack Real Red makes it easier  with protected, padded storage for a laptop, and just enough organization.', 'laptop backpack, osprey, daylite plus, travel pack', 2, 3, '2018-01-26 19:52:24'),
(17, 'Osprey Farpoint 40L M/L Travel Pack Volcanic Grey', '10000298-VG', '<p>Ospreyâs Farpoint 40 is perfect for a weekend getaway in the city or the wilderness. The LightWireâ¢ frame suspension transfers the load from harness to hipbelt. A mesh backpanel improves ventilation and the mesh on the harness and hipbelt reduces chafing under load. The entire suspension stows away under a zippered panel creating a sleek silhouette for transport. </p>', '<p>Unzip the lockable sliders to access the main compartment. Inside thereâs a mesh pocket for small items. Dual compression straps keep cargo from shifting during transit. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Outside youâll find a zippered front panel slash pocket to keep you organized and sewn attachment points to lash on extra gear. No matter how much you choose to carry, StraightJacketâ¢ compression straps stabilize the load. The padded top and side handles give you purchase when you need to toss the Farpoint 40 into the back of the bus.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Volcanic Grey</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 1438 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 40 L</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 53 x 33 x 23 cm</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Fixed, unisex backpanel, hipbelt and harness system can easily be stowed and zipped away for a slimmer profile when traveling. The creates a slimmer profile for the bag, making it a better checked bag</li>\r\n  <li>Large panel zip access to main compartment with lockable sliders provides accessibility and security to main contents </li>\r\n  <li>Top and side padded carry handles are helpful when you need to hoist the pack</li>\r\n  <li>Dual front compression straps keep gear stable while wearing the pack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Fabric</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Main: 210D Nylon Mini Hex Diamond Ripstop</li>\r\n  <li>Accent: 600D Packcloth</li>\r\n  <li>B