(25, 'Craghoppers Men\'s Kiwi Interactive Jacket Black', 'CMA1135R-B-L', '<p>Our fabulously practical microfleece jacket is a great standalone but is also designed to interact perfectly with Kiwi Jackets, providing a handy extra layer of insulation when it is needed.</p>', '<p>Constructed from top quality, fast drying, lightweight fleece fabric, it incorporates snug handwarmer pockets and a full length. The classic fleece for everyday adventures.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Color: </strong> Black</p>\r\n<p class=\"orange\"><strong>Please refer to the images for the sizing guide</strong></p>\r\n<img src=\"assets/img/catalog/craghoppers-sizing-guide.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\">', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Wash &amp; Wear</li>\r\n  <li>Lightweight</li>\r\n  <li>Full length interactive zip</li>\r\n  <li>2 welted zipped lower pockets</li>\r\n</ul>', '3300.00', 9, 'assets/img/products/craghoppers-men-s-kiwi-interactive-jacket-black.jpg', 'Craghoppers Men\'s Kiwi Interactive Jacket Black', 'Our fabulously practical microfleece jacket is a great standalone but is also designed to interact perfectly with Kiwi Jackets, providing a handy extra layer of insulation when it is needed.', 'craghoppers, kiwi jacket, kiwi, microfleece jacket', 1, 6, '2018-01-26 21:43:12'),
