(39, 'Vargo Titanium BOT - 700', 'T-466', '<p>Hydrate while you hike</p>', '<p>Decrease cooking times, meal waiting times, and fuel usage with the BOT - 700! Its watertight screw-top lid and 700 ml volume is perfect for pre-soaking your dehydrated and freeze-dried meals for easier and tastier results. It can also carry, cook, measure, store, and hold almost whatever you want it to. It\'ll become your go-to companion for every trip.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Diameter: </strong> 10.5 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 125g </p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 16.5 x 9.9 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 700 ml</p>\r\n<p><strong>Height: </strong> 12.2 cm</p>', '', '7000.00', 3, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-bot-700.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium BOT - 700', 'Vargo Titanium BOT - 700\'s watertight screw-top lid and 700 ml volume is perfect for pre-soaking your dehydrated and freeze-dried meals for easier and tastier results.', 'vargo, titanium, titanium bot, cookware, camping', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:07:56'),
(40, 'Vargo Titanium Converter Stove', 'T-307', '<p>Convert the Hexagon Wood Stove* into a complete multi-fuel stove with our titanium Converter Stove. </p>', '<p>Its easy âdrop-inâ design turns the Hexagon into an effective windscreen while providing the ideal distance between stove and cookware for optimal cooking efficiency. Unlike other stoves, the Converter Stove will cook faster and won\'t leave soot on the bottom of your pots. Burns alcohol, fuel tabs, fuel gels. Simply flip the stove over to switch between alcohol and fuel tab/gel burning modes. The folding stand allows for compact packing and use as a standalone stove.</p>\r\n<p class=\"red\"><em>*Hexagon Wood Stove sold separately</em></p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Stove diameter: </strong> 6.1 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stove height: </strong> 3.2cm </p>\r\n<p><strong>Stand diameter &#40;open&#41;: </strong> 10.7 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stand height: </strong> 3.2 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 48 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 59 ml</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>All titanium contstruction</li>\r\n  <li>Converts the Hexagon Wood Stove into a complete multi-fuel stove system</li>\r\n  <li>Use as a standalone alcohol and fuel tab/gel stove</li>\r\n  <li>Easily switches between alcohol and fuel tab/gel burning modes</li>\r\n  <li>Fold flat stand </li>\r\n  <li>Convenient carrying case</li>\r\n</ul>', '2500.00', 4, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-converter-stove.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Converter Stove', 'Convert the Vargo Titanium Converter Stove into a complete multi-fuel stove with our titanium Converter Stove.', 'vargo, camping stove, converter stove, outdoor stove, portable stove', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:17:31'),
(41, 'Vargo Titanium Fire Box Grill', 'T-433', '<p>Get grillinâ in the backcountry without charring the Earth or weighing down your pack!</p>', '<p> The Fire Box Grill features a hinged grate and panel system for easy setup, fold-flat packing, and fire preparation. Just lift the grate and add your fuel. Titanium tent stake skewered kebabs, anyone?</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Burn Time: </strong> Indefinite</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 164 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 20.5x 20.5 x 8 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stainless Steel: </strong> 284 g</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Burns biomass fuel</li>\r\n  <li>Folds flat</li>\r\n  <li>Hinged grate</li>\r\n  <li>Easy setup</li>\r\n  <li>Fold flat stand </li>\r\n  <li>Nylon carrying case</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '5400.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-fire-box-grill.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Fire Box Grill', 'The Vargo Titanium Fire Box Grill features a hinged grate and panel system for easy setup, fold-flat packing, and fire preparation. ', 'grill, vargo, fire box grill, titanium grill', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:23:20'),
(42, 'Vargo Stainless Steel BOT - Bottle Pot', 'T-437', '<p>Stop carrying (and paying for) a water bottle AND cooking pot--the Stainless Steel BOT is made to replace both! </p>', '<p>Half water bottle, half cooking pot, it performs both functions exceptionally well while weighing less than the combined weight of a separate water bottle and cooking pot. It converts easily from a water bottle to a cooking pot with a simple flip of the lid yet its watertight, temperature resistant O-ring wonât melt when exposed to heat.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 1 L</p>\r\n<p><strong>Outer Diameter: </strong> 10.5 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Inner Diameter: </strong> 9.6 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Height: </strong> 16 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 238 g</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>High quality Grade 304 stainlesss steel construction</li>\r\n  <li>1 liter capacity (34 oz)</li>\r\n  <li>Food safe</li>\r\n  <li>Unlined, uncoated material</li>\r\n  <li>Lid doubles as water bottle and cooking lid </li>\r\n  <li>Water tight, heat resistant O-ring</li>\r\n  <li>Wide mouth</li>\r\n  <li>Fits in most water bottle pockets</li>\r\n  <li>Pot lifter compatible</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2600.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-bot-700.jpg', 'Vargo Stainless Steel BOT - Bottle Pot', 'Stop carrying (and paying for) a water bottle AND cooking pot--the Vargo Stainless Steel BOT - Bottle Pot is made to replace both! ', 'vargo, water bottle, cooking pot, cookware, steel bot, bottle pot', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:34:53'),
(43, 'Vargo Titanium Spork - Ultralight Blue', 'T-203', '<p>Our Vargo Titanium Spork is still an original! Dubbed by many as âthe perfectâ spork, no ultralight backpacker should be without one.</p>', '<p>Four available colors help prevent it from being lost and is a fun way to know which one is yours. Just another Vargo original idea.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Size: </strong> 16.2 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 14 g</p>\r\n', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Polished finish</li>\r\n  <li>Made of pure titanium</li>\r\n  <li>Biocompatible</li>\r\n  <li>Available in Natural, Blue, Lavender, and Yellow</li>\r\n</ul>', '700.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-spork-ultralight-blue.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Spork - Ultralight Blue', 'Vargo Titanium Spork - Ultralight Blue is still an original! Dubbed by many as âthe perfectâ spork, no ultralight backpacker should be without one.', 'vargo, spork, titanium spork, cutlery', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:39:21'),
(44, 'Vargo Aluminium windscreen Blue', 'T-420', '<p>Designed for use with our ultralight alcohol stoves, the Aluminum Windscreen has top and bottom cut-outs for proper ventilation and flame management. </p>', '<p>For DIY alcohol stove makers the windscreen can also serve as a light load pot support.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 41.6 x 8.1 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 38 g</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>One piece, fold flat design</li>\r\n  <li>Cut outs for proper ventilation</li>\r\n  <li>Light load pot support capability</li>\r\n  <li>Aluminum construction</li>\r\n</ul>', '800.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/vargo-aluminium-windscreen-blue.jpg', 'Vargo Aluminium windscreen Blue', 'Vargo Aluminium windscreen Blue has top and bottom cut-outs for proper ventilation and flame management. ', 'vargo, windscreen, camping stove, stove screen', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:42:50'),
(45, 'Vargo Titanium Pot 1.3 Liter', 'T-426', '<p>Our Vargo 1.3 Liter Titanium Pot is our largest pot, yet it weighs in just north of 5 oz. making it almost half the weight of other similar sized pots. </p>', '<p>And with built-in, coated handles and the Vargo original strainer lid, itâs twice as functional.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 15.7 x 8.9 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 153 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 1.3 L</p>', ' \r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Ultralight titanium construction</li>\r\n  <li>1.3 liter capacity &#40;44 oz&#41;</li>\r\n  <li>Biocompatible</li>\r\n  <li>Vargo original strainer lid</li>\r\n  <li>Coated foldaway handles</li>\r\n  <li>Mesh storage bag</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '5000.00', 3, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-pot-1-3-liter.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Pot 1.3 Liter', 'Our Vargo 1.3 Liter Titanium Pot is our largest pot, yet it weighs in just north of 5 oz. making it almost half the weight of other similar sized pots.', 'vargo, titanium pot, cookware,  camping pot', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:47:00'),
(46, 'Vargo Triad Multi-Fuel Stove', 'T-305', '<p>Cooking versatility has never been so light! For a scant ounce, the Vargo Triad Multi-Fuel Stove pairs multi-fuel performance with the strength, durability, and weight savings of titanium.</p>', '<p>Used upright, the Triad is a quick filling, long burning alcohol stove. Or, flipped over, it burns fuel tabs or fuel gels for additional fuel options. Get more capability for less weight with the Triad Multi-Fuel Stove.</p>\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Diameter: </strong> 8.9cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 30 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Burn time: </strong> ~20 mins alcohol, ~12 mins fuel tabs, various for fuel gels</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Solid titanium construction</li>\r\n  <li>Multi-fuel capability</li>\r\n  <li>All-season, all-terrain useability</li>\r\n  <li>Folding legs and pot supports</li>\r\n  <li>Fast filling and easy to reclaim unused fuel</li>\r\n  <li>Simple to use, minimal maintenance, compact, and reliable</li>\r\n</ul>', '2000.00', 6, 'assets/img/products/vargo-triad-multi-fuel-stove.jpg', 'Vargo Triad Multi-Fuel Stove', 'For a scant ounce, the Vargo Triad Multi-Fuel Stove pairs multi-fuel performance with the strength, durability, and weight savings of titanium.', 'vargo, triad stove, camping stove, multi-fuel stove, outdoor stove, cookware', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:51:41'),
(47, 'Vargo Titanium Ti-lite Mug (750 ml)', 'T-401', '<p>The Titanium Ti-Lite 750 Mug is one of our most popular, versatile products and is now over an ounce lighter than the original. </p>', '<p>Large enough to cook single entree meals yet small and compact enough to enjoy an early morning cup of coffee or tea while fitting anywhere in your pack. It even fits a 32 oz. Nalgene bottle inside for easy packing.  Your ultralight cook system starts here!</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 9.6 x 10.5 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 117 g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Capacity: </strong> 750 ml</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Ultralight titanium construction</li>\r\n  <li>750 ml capacity &#40;25 oz&#41;</li>\r\n  <li>Graduated measurements</li>\r\n  <li>Biocompatible</li>\r\n  <li>Vargo original strainer lid</li>\r\n  <li>Foldaway handles</li>\r\n  <li>Stay cool rim</li>\r\n  <li>Mesh storage bag</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '3700.00', 2, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-ti-lite-mug-750-ml.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Ti-lite Mug (750 ml)', 'The Titanium Ti-Lite 750 Mug is one of our most popular, versatile products and is now over an ounce lighter than the original.', 'vargo, titanium, ti-lite, ti-lite 750 mug', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 19:57:25'),
(48, 'Vargo Titanium Pot Lifter', 'T-419', '<p>The ULTRA-lightweight Vargo Titanium Pot Lifter provides excellent grip control and pot grabbing capability yet weighs less than 1 ounce.</p>', '<p>We removed all unnecessary material in the handle to give you everything you need and nothing you donât. With its titanium construction, itâs quite simply one of the lightest and most durable pot lifters on the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Size: </strong> 12.6 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 23  g</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Extremely lightweight</li>\r\n  <li>Works with most pots and pans</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '1600.00', 1, 'assets/img/products/vargo-titanium-pot-lifter.jpg', 'Vargo Titanium Pot Lifter', 'The Vargo Titanium Pot Lifter provides excellent grip control and pot grabbing capability yet weighs less than 1 ounce.', 'vargo, titanium pot lifter, pot lifter', 4, 1, '2018-01-27 20:02:25'),
(49, 'Ferrino Dream Self Inflating Mat', '78201V', '<p>In hardwearing 190 T polyester fabric with foam resin. Complete with stuff sack, repair kit and elastic containment straps.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 183 x 51 x 3.5 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 1100  g</p>', '', '2400.00', 3, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-dream-self-inflating-mat.jpg', 'Ferrino Dream Self Inflating Mat', 'Ferrino Dream Self Inflating Mat  is complete with stuff sack, repair kit and elastic containment straps', 'ferrino, mat, self inflating mat, ferrino dream, sleeping mat', 6, 2, '2018-01-27 20:21:10'),
(50, 'Ferrino Rider Pro', '86369', '<p>Thermal cover and survival bag in ripstop polyester, coated in heat-insulating, aluminised material with taped lining.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 230 x 80 x 50 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 260  g</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Features</p></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Waterproof</li>\r\n  <li>Extra-roomy mummy shape for easy access</li>\r\n  <li>Complete with central zipper and zipper in the feet area for excellent ventilation</li>\r\n</ul>', '2000.00', 4, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-rider-pro.jpg', 'Ferrino Rider Pro', 'Ferrino Rider Pro is a thermal cover and survival bag in ripstop polyester, coated in heat-insulating, aluminised material with taped lining.', 'ferribo, sleeping bag, thermal cover', 6, 2, '2018-01-27 20:33:25'),
(51, 'Ferrino Swift Inflatable Mattress 50', '78220CCC', '<p>Polyester fabric made of 23 horizontal tubes. Foot pump included.</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 183 x 50 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 700  g</p>', '', '4500.00', 3, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-swift-inflatable-mattress-50.jpg', 'Ferrino Swift Inflatable Mattress 50', 'Polyester fabric made of 23 horizontal tubes. Foot pump included.', 'ferrino, sleeping mat, ferrino swift, swift inflatable mattress, swift 50', 6, 2, '2018-01-27 20:38:23'),
