(53, 'Ferrino Sleepingbag Lightech SM 1100 Blue', '86650EBB ', '<p>These sleeping bags with extremely reduced size and weight offer excellent heat performance thanks to the shingle construction</p>', '<strong><p class=\"orange\">Specifications</p></strong>\r\n<p><strong>Dimensions: </strong> 215 x 80 x 50  cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Weight: </strong> 1100  g</p>\r\n<p><strong>Volume: </strong> 18 x 37 cm</p>\r\n<p><strong>Temperature: </strong> -20 / - 3 / 2 / 18 &deg;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Inner: </strong> 100% Polyester </p>\r\n<p><strong>Ext: </strong> 100% 260T Ripstop Polyester </p>\r\n<p><strong>Filling: </strong> 120- 60 g/sqm H.T.F. Compact</p>', '', '5400.00', 5, 'assets/img/products/ferrino-sleepingbag-lightech-sm-1100-blue.jpg', 'Ferrino Sleepingbag Lightech SM 1100 Blue', 'Ferrino Sleepingbag Lightech SM 1100 Blue offers excellent heat performance thanks to the shingle construction.', 'ferrino, lightweight sleeping bag, sleeping bag, lightech sm 1100', 6, 2, '2018-01-27 20:56:41'),
